sourcesContent: import { ChangeDetectionStrategy, Component, Input } from "@angular/core"; @Component({ selector: "app-icon-button", templateUrl: "./icon-button.component.html", styleUrls: ["./icon-button.component.scss"], changeDetection: ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush, }) export class IconButtonComponent { @Input() style: "Filled" | "Outlined" | "Standard" | "Tonal" = "Outlined"; @Input() state: "Enabled" | "Hovered" | "Focused" | "Pressed" | "Disabled" = "Disabled"; }
